Fold Space		CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:ForcePower.SpecialQuality		DESC:You can use The Force to bend space, transporting an object almost instantaneously from one place to another. Make a Use the Force check. The result of the check determines the maximum size of the object you can transport, and the distance you can transport it: Special: If the object you are transporting contains other objects or creatures (such as a Starship), everything contained within the object is transported as well.

You can spend a Force Point to increase the maximum size of the object you can move by two categories, up to Colossal (Cruiser) in size, or double the distance the object is transported.